&lt;li&gt;Understands codes and standards and has ability to research code issues, present interpretation, and properly apply in the daily work.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Performs Life Safety and Code Analysis and prepare Life Safety Plans.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Has an excellent understanding and knowledge of construction techniques and constructability.&lt;/li&gt;
