&lt;li&gt;Assists in preparing design budgets, marketing proposals and cost estimates.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist in client contact and communication pertaining to specific projects.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Promote communications, cooperation and quality among staff.&lt;/li&gt;
