ental approvals, and licenses.&lt;br&gt;• &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;Leading a strong safety and quality program on the project.&lt;br&gt;• &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;Leading the commissioning, closeout, and turnover process.&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
